      <data key="d3">69.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Tenants must adhere to the conditions outlined in rental agreements, which detail their rights and responsibilities in the rental relationship."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Tenant is governed by the Rental Agreement, which outlines their rights and obligations within the rental property."&lt;SEP&gt;"The rental agreement outlines the obligations and rights of the tenant, binding them to comply with its terms."|&lt;|"contractual obligations, rights"&lt;SEP&gt;"The rental agreement outlines the terms and conditions that the tenant agrees to follow while renting the property."&lt;SEP&gt;"The rental agreement stipulates the terms under which a tenant occupies a dwelling unit, guiding the relationship."&lt;SEP&gt;"The tenant is bound by the terms and conditions set out in the rental agreement with the landlord."&lt;SEP&gt;"The tenant is bound by the terms of the rental agreement that defines their rights and obligations concerning the rental property."&lt;SEP&gt;"The tenant's rights and obligations are defined by the rental agreement they enter into with the landlord."</data>
      <data key="d5">"contractual agreement, tenancy terms"&lt;SEP&gt;"contractual obligation, legal compliance"&lt;SEP&gt;"contractual obligations, rights"&lt;SEP&gt;"contractual obligations, tenant rights"&lt;SEP&gt;"contractual obligations, terms of lease"&lt;SEP&gt;"contractual terms, rights"&lt;SEP&gt;"rights and obligations, legal contract"&lt;SEP&gt;9</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-c3bc1dbbc22da4bbc6a6de45ffaa66df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6545ef03dc8e11cfc621983d50e00f5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-948f888104b901aa818d8a64425e31e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7759df7263a7c6a25e1e83bd43ddc9c9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-caa542bbeffaceb300226b5da0f70961&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-49eeebcde41c80ab078e5fdc2db008fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-471bca0f3da3db4a8af4c1624c74f5ad&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d2157989b5839c3e9aeb71adca8d9db4</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;RENTAL AGREEMENT&quot;" target="&quot;LANDLORD&quot;">
      <data key="d3">52.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Rental agreements are the formal contracts established by landlords setting terms for the tenant's occupation of a property."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Landlord enters into a Rental Agreement with the Tenant that governs the terms of the lease, including security deposits."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Landlord is bound by the terms of the Rental Agreement, which governs the obligations they must fulfill towards the Tenant."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Landlord is responsible for adhering to the terms of the Rental Agreement, which stipulates the conditions of the tenancy."&lt;SEP&gt;"The landlord creates the rental agreement that outlines the conditions under which a tenant may occupy the rental property."&lt;SEP&gt;"The rental agreement serves as the legal framework defining the landlord's rights and responsibilities regarding the property."|&lt;|"legal framework, rights and responsibilities"</data>
      <data key="d5">"contractual creation, legal framework"&lt;SEP&gt;"contractual nature, obligations"&lt;SEP&gt;"contractual obligation, governance"&lt;SEP&gt;"contractual obligation, rental terms"&lt;SEP&gt;"obligations, legal contract"&lt;SEP&gt;8</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-c3bc1dbbc22da4bbc6a6de45ffaa66df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6545ef03dc8e11cfc621983d50e00f5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-948f888104b901aa818d8a64425e31e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-471bca0f3da3db4a8af4c1624c74f5ad&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bc145ddced779a4e72a5f21656d00d2e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bbf2a304267f411fdd75632601e64887</data>
    </edge>
